## [0.2.0] - 22.12.2022

### Added

- Character Sprite with Animation
- Startmenu
- Option menu
- Leaderboard menu
- Weapon system
- Attribute system
- DataBase Connection
- ShopSystem
- Bullet sprites
- Exp. and Currency system
- Wave System

### Changed

- Pause menu

### Fixed

- Enemy Spawning system, enemies aren't spawing in the character anymore



## [0.3.0] - 22.01.2023

### Added

- Enemy sprites and animation
- Boss spwans in the 3rd Wave 
- Boss sprites and animation
- Selfcreated Music Theme
- Slider Volume for Music
- Floor in game
- Login and create Account function
- view highscore
- Health bar
- Exp bar
- Enemies drop Currency and Exp
- Health script for Character
- actication.yml
- Item proabillity
- different Weapon lvls
- bullet sprites

### Changed

- singleton pattern for Weapon Inventory
- Weapon system (added weapon fetcher and superclasses)

### Fixed

- Redudancy in weapon system

## [0.4.0] - 12.02.2023

### Added

- attribute leveling
- icons for attribues
- leveling attributes
- path constants
- clean codes -> readonly clrasses for string constants
- factories, interface, abstract class for character

### Changed 

- balanced currency drop from enemies
- balanced shop prices and reroll prices
- value calculation for weapons

### Fixed 

- legendary items never showed up in Shop
- weapons were not removed in shop
- exp and currency collect range

